Sandra Smith (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sandra_Smith_(actor) 0 Sandra Smith (born June 27, 1940, in Minneapolis, Minnesota) is an American actress known for her roles on American television shows. She was a member of the cast of The Interns and once guest-starred on Star Trek.
